{"tid":699487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"納粹鐵蹄佔領全歐洲之時，英國首相邱吉爾勉勵國民：絕不屈服   也絕不投降","createTime":"2018-06-12T14:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T18:39:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a81f17be122adf093486e053aea9e1b896b11945","tid":699487,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20150718/photo/bknint-20150718173408513-0718_17011_001_04b.jpg?20150718214238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150718%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20150718173408513-0718_17011_001_04b.jpg%3F20150718214238&h=606fa158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倫敦大轟炸持續了267天，摧毁數百萬房屋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.23yy.com/upload/2017/10/23/fb102ad029876c0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.23yy.com%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F23%2Ffb102ad029876c0a.jpg&h=11ce21cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決不屈服，決不屈服，決不，決不，決不，決不 &mdash;&mdash; 除了對於榮譽和智慧的信念，不向任何事物低頭，不管是宏大還是渺小，不管是重要還是瑣碎。<br />\n<br />\nNever give in. Never give in. Never, never, never, never &mdash; in nothing, great or small, large or petty&mdash;never give in, except to convictions of honour and good sense. Never yield to force. Never yield to the apparently overwhelming might of the enemy.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們將不惜一切犧牲保衛我國本土，我們要在灘頭作戰，在登陸地作戰，在田野、在山上、在街頭作戰，我們在任何時候決不投降，即使整個英倫島或大部分土地被占，我們饑寒交迫，我們所有由英國艦隊武裝和保護的海外帝國也將繼續戰鬥。<br />\n<br />\nWe shall defend our Island, whatever the cost may be, we shall fight on the beaches, we shall fight on the landing grounds, we shall fight in the fields and in the streets, we shall fight in the hills; we shall never surrender."},{"pid":"4ef7c59144fc649d6e899b9b2f3568dedc7a6605","tid":699487,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.afwing.com/d/file/aircraft/others/uk/507748720b745cd18c82ee041266bc53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afwing.com%2Fd%2Ffile%2Faircraft%2Fothers%2Fuk%2F507748720b745cd18c82ee041266bc53.jpg&h=59cc4f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你們問我們的目標是什麼我可以用一個單詞來回答：勝利，以一切代價去贏得勝利，無論勝利來的多麼恐怖無論道路多麼遙遠和艱辛，沒有勝利就不可能有生存。<br />\n<br />\nYou ask, what is our policy? I can say: It is to wage war, by sea, land and air, with all our might and with all the strength that God can give us: to wage war against a monstrous tyranny, never surpassed in the dark, lamentable catalogue of human crime. That is our policy. You ask, what is our aim? I can answer in one word: It is victory, victory at all costs, victory in spite of all terror, victory, however long and hard the road may be; for without victory, there is no survival."},{"pid":"0db00cbba7bd18267a842940ced7d1b39dd41cbc","tid":699487,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"現在並不是結束，結束甚至還沒有開始。但是現在可能是序幕的結束。<br />\n<br />\nNow this is not the end. It is not even the beginning of the end. But it is, perhaps, the end of the beginning.<br />\n<br />\n- 邱吉爾爵士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180611/large/1528686812_2ce8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180611%2Flarge%2F1528686812_2ce8.jpg&h=b4dd2b09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dffac12338d2861bfa6213358edf1115253817ab","tid":699487,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e1ae0f916f46bed6fe7d51beed4515718feedbe","tid":699487,"uid":134323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"we shall never surrender <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7974a3253fef8050d6bcef723df841ca45b70174","tid":699487,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"所有英國國民都應該重新謹記騎士精神<br />\n<br />\nI will be kind to the weak. <br />\n<br />\nI will be brave against the strong. <br />\n<br />\nI will fight all who do wrong. <br />\n<br />\nI will fight for those who cannot fight. <br />\n <br />\nI will help those who call me for help. <br />\n<br />\nI will harm no woman. <br />\n<br />\nI will help my brother knight. <br />\n<br />\nI will be true to my friends. <br />\n<br />\nI will be faithful in love."},{"pid":"27f22fe876d7bdb1d51cd16de257217032866abf","tid":699487,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dffac12338d2861bfa6213358edf1115253817ab","tid":699487,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 九唔搭八"},{"pid":"931c635310e8a98464885e6f31222fd8c40dedc8","tid":699487,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7d5c05067f259174f2aa35a095435050a50f8b1","tid":699487,"uid":36964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"931c635310e8a98464885e6f31222fd8c40dedc8","tid":699487,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"dffac12338d2861bfa6213358edf1115253817ab","tid":699487,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"係啦<br />\n講都唔好講最實際 乜都唔好做 諗都唔好諗"},{"pid":"1ac78d5b4ad73c6655158eb7742b53b1f360fd8d","tid":699487,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:58:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c94ed6d4d82366ba84eb597b8ba87325ae937640","tid":699487,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b819c1c1afeebc04d8e6ac1bceb099fc72